{"article_id":"yddj1XsLlK6TrU02","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Hagel decision appeals to Obama 's bipartisan spirit .","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Why Obama picked Hagel","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"President Barack Obama ' s decision","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"to nominate Chuck Hagel as secretary of defense","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"has mystified lawmakers from both parties .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Democrats don ' t love the former Nebraska senator","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"because he ' s a Republican .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Republicans don ' t think","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"he ' s a real Republican .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"And his past statements have at times angered two key Obama constituencies :","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Jewish groups and gay-rights activists .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"But inside the White House , the choice makes sense .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"It appeals to Obama ' s bipartisan spirit","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"- and the optics aren ' t bad , either -","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to have any Republican as Defense secretary","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"when Obama is seeking to end the war in Afghanistan","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and dramatically reduce the Pentagon ' s budget .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Hagel brings even more credibility to the task","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"because he ' s a decorated Vietnam veteran","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"and would be the first from that war","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"to lead the Pentagon .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"Hagel also has long-standing relationships with Obama and Vice President Joe Biden","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"dating to their time in the Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and he ' s a particularly close friend of Biden ' s .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Defense isn ' t the first high-level post","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"the White House has discussed with Hagel :","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"An individual","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"who speaks regularly with Hagel","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"the White House has spoken with him about becoming Commerce secretary and CIA director , among other jobs .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"During Obama ' s first term , Hagel has been in regular contact with the White House on foreign policy issues as co-chairman of Obama ' s Intelligence Advisory Board and a member of outgoing Defense Secretary Leon Panetta ' s Defense Policy Board .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"There ' s still no evidence","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that any Democratic senators will vote against an Obama-nominated Hagel ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and tradition holds","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that senators get an easy ride","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"when up for Cabinet posts .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Despite the vocal objections of a few GOP senators ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"only three have explicitly said","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"they will vote against Hagel .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Hagel cost himself capital among Republicans","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"for bucking party orthodoxy ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"but the White House is prepared for a fight over the GOP ' s past foreign policy positions .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" If at the end of the day these guys are frustrated","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that he had the courage","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"to buck his party on the Iraq War ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"that ' s going to be a tough case","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"to make to the American people , \"","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"White House spokesman Tommy Vietor said .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Longtime Obama confidant and political adviser David Axelrod tweeted Sunday night","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"that \" Attacks on Hagel r bogus .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"He ' s tough , courageous , sensible & able to withstand political pressure","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"to do what ' s right for USA .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"What we need ! \"","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Mike Buttry , Hagel ' s former chief of staff , previewed","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"how Hagel might defend himself against criticism by GOP senators during the confirmation process .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"Buttry said","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Hagel is \" not blind \" to the opposition to his nomination .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"\" He always just did what he thought was right .","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"He always was trying to do what he thought was the right thing","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"and never gave much thought into how it might be received , \"","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Buttry told Sunday .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"\" He ' s thinking about ,","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"' What do I have to do","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to do this job the best way","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"I can do it ? ' \"","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Both Obama and Biden have traveled to war zones with Hagel - Obama during his summer 2008 Iraq and Afghanistan trips as the Democratic presidential nominee .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"But Hagel ' s relationship with Biden runs much deeper and is more personal , a result of their 12-year bond","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"from serving together in the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"including on the Foreign Relations Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Buttry said .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"\" They ' re just friends ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"they ' re very close , \"","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Buttry said of Hagel and Biden .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"\" They ' ve traveled together ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"their families get along .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"There ' s just a closeness there .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"They ' ve worked on legislation together .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"It ' s like any kind of friendship ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"they ' re just two guys","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"who clicked together . \"","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"For the White House , the political dynamics","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"surrounding the Hagel nomination are different than those for Susan Rice , another longtime friend of Obama","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"who removed herself from consideration for secretary of state in December ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"she said ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"to spare the president .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"She was concerned","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Republican anger over her role in the Benghazi attacks would distract from his second-term agenda .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"\" It was clear from early on that many in Congress , especially Republicans , were going to make a witch hunt and an example out of Susan Rice , \"","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"a person close to Obama said .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"\" I think","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"that the Rice case was obviously a case","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"where it would seemingly have been an insurmountable challenge . \"","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"White House officials said","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Hagel has a clearer path toward confirmation .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"Still , a major fight over Hagel could lead to many of the same distractions","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"Rice sought to avoid","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"- tripping up other major items on the president ' s agenda ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"including immigration , the economy and now gun control .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Obama has made the calculation","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that the long-term benefits are worth the immediate battle .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"The White House believes","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Hagel ' s Senate record will overcome trouble about controversial statements","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Hagel has made ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"such as his 2006 reference to a \" Jewish lobby. \"","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Talking points","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"dated Dec. 19","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"- written","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"and being circulated in Washington by Hagel allies -","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"say","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"he has \" an unbroken record of substantive support for Israel . \"","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Axelrod wrote Sunday","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"\" supporters of Israel ,","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"of which I am one ,","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"also make a huge mistake","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"by depicting Hagel as hostile .","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"No such evidence in his record . \"","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"Democrats also are counting on a bipartisan tradition with regard to foreign policy .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Obama ' s New START agreement ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"which reduced the number of nuclear missile launchers in the United States and Russia ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"won 71 votes during the 2010 lame duck session .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"A Democratic official","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"who believes","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"Hagel will be confirmed","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"stressed","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"once he is formally nominated ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"the Nebraskan will have enthusiastic support from veterans organizations .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Hagel would be the first defense secretary","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"who served as an enlisted man","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"- an idea","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"that will be popular with the troops ,","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"the official said ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"and Hagel ' s defenders are sure to emphasize","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"that he earned two Purple Hearts","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"and still carries shrapnel in his chest .","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"That record ,","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"Obama ' s allies say ,","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"gives Hagel credibility as a leader","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"who can cut Pentagon spending","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"and bring home American troops from overseas .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"\" This is a challenging time in the world ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"and there are going to be tough cuts","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"that need to be made , \"","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"said Jen Psaki , Obama ' s campaign spokeswoman .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"\" One of the tasks of the next secretary of defense is to see that through ,","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"and clearly Mr. Hagel is somebody","depth":14},{"id":147,"text":"who has been through it .","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"He ' s been there on the front lines ,","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"he ' s been there in prominent positions in Congress on the Foreign Relations Committee ,","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"and he has the reputation","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"of having the balance","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"needed for this job . \"","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"White House officials said","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"they are not concerned","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"that Hagel ' s 1998 comments about James Hormel , an openly gay nominee","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"to be President Bill Clinton ' s U.S. ambassador to Luxembourg ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"will trouble Hagel ' s confirmation ,","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"given his recent apology for them .","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"Human Rights Campaign President Chad Griffin said last month","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"that he accepted Hagel ' s words of regret .","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"Vietor said Sunday","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"that Hagel is not alone","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"in having changed his position on gay issues .","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"\" I think","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"that a lot of people have had their views evolve on LGBT issues over the last 20 years , \"","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"Vietor said .","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"\" At the time","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"he made those comments ,","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"you had a Democratic president sign ' don ' t ask , don ' t tell ' and [ the Defense of Marriage Act ] into law . \"","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"On Capitol Hill , both Democrats and Republicans questioned the Hagel strategy ,","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"asking","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"why Obama would go to the wall for a Republican","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"but allow momentum against Rice to build past the point of no return .","depth":14},{"id":174,"text":"\" It is a strange signal for the White House to send","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"that they are willing to fight for Hagel but not Rice , \"","depth":13},{"id":176,"text":"one Senate Democratic aide said .","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"\" Democrats are not currently unified behind Hagel ,","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"and it will take some real work by the administration to get them there ,","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"if it ' s even possible . \"","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"Senior Republicans said","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"there is no natural base for Hagel","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"despite his years in the Senate .","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"\" I can ' t imagine why","depth":14},{"id":184,"text":"[ Obama ] would choose to burn his political capital on this nomination .","depth":14},{"id":185,"text":"For what ?","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"There is no constituency for Chuck Hagel , \"","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"one senior GOP aide said .","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"\" Obama will expend every ounce of political capital","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"he has","depth":14},{"id":190,"text":"to get him across the finish line .","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"Dems will hate this . \"","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"Allies of Obama and Hagel said Sunday","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"that only a few GOP senators","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"- John Cornyn and Ted Cruz of Texas and Tom Coburn of Oklahoma -","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"have committed to voting against Hagel ' s confirmation ,","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"though Lindsey Graham of South Carolina also expressed strong reservations .","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell of Kentucky pledged a \" fair hearing \" for Hagel ,","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"passing on opportunities","depth":13},{"id":199,"text":"to denounce his nomination or his past statements about Israel .","depth":13},{"id":200,"text":"\" I think","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"he ought to be given a fair hearing like any other nominee ,","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"and he will be , \"","depth":13},{"id":203,"text":"McConnell said on ABC ' s \" This Week. \"","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"\" I ' m going to wait","depth":11},{"id":205,"text":"and see","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"how the hearings go","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"and whether Chuck ' s views square with the job","depth":14},{"id":208,"text":"he would be nominated to do . \"","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"Axelrod ' s Sunday posts on Twitter reminded McConnell of his own past comments .","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"\" McConnell was right a few years [ ago ]","depth":12},{"id":211,"text":"when he called Hagel ' a great statesmen , ' \"","depth":12},{"id":212,"text":"Axelrod wrote .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":425,"left":0,"right":424,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":424,"left":264,"right":423,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":264,"left":1,"right":263,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":263,"left":241,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":222,"right":240,"relat